meta.name: Text to Speech (Save to File)
meta.description: Converts text to speech using ElevenLabs API and saves the output to as a file on BuildShip Storage and gives a publically accessible URL.

meta.name: Text to Speech (Base64 Buffer)
meta.description: Converts text to speech using ElevenLabs API and returns the Base64 encoded audio buffer data

meta.name: Stream TTS Audio
meta.description:
Converts a stream of text to a stream of speech using ElevenLabs API.

The speech stream is mp3 encoded.
